{"data":[{"date":"18:06 02/07","title":"PSG s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng si\u00eau th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/18/psg-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sieu-thu-mon-vao-tuan-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gianluigi Buffon t\u1edbi PSG v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Gianluigi Buffon</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/chia-tay-juventus-buffon-hoi-cai-mot-chuyen-184-186551.html\" target=\"_blank\">Gianluigi Buffon x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chia tay Juventus</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3. Ng\u00f4i sao 40 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u1ed1t th\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Gianluigi Buffon t\u1edbi PSG  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u1ed1t th\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Gianluigi Buffon t\u1edbi PSG  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/18/psg-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sieu-thu-mon-vao-tuan-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Buffon\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGianluigi Buffon v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao th\u00eam 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00ecm CLB m\u1edbi ngay sau khi chia tay Juventus.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Gianluigi Buffon nh\u1ea5t. Alphonse Areola l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a PSG \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i\u00a0s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Buffon \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00e0 s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Buffon s\u1ebd t\u1edbi PSG v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gianluigi Buffon t\u1edbi PSG v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Buffon\" title=\"thu mon Buffon\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/17/Gianluigi-Buffon-roi-Juventus-sau-mua-201718-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Buffon v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb L'Equipe kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Buffon, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 40 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris. V\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Buffon, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Alphonse Areola ho\u1eb7c Kevin Trapp s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Italia ho\u1eb7c Ligue 1 quan t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Buffon c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c, nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Champions League thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 ho\u1eb7c ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3946","checkdouble":"190190"},{"date":"19:23 02/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 2/7: M\u1edbi nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c, HLV Bayern \u0111\u00e3 gieo s\u1ea7u cho Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-27-ngay-dau-nham-chuc-hlv-bayern-da-gieo-sau-cho-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 2/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Welbeck ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. </strong>Danny Welbeck mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Colombia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Tam s\u01b0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nguy hi\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c, HLV Bayern \u0111\u00e3 gieo s\u1ea7u cho Real. </strong>Niko Kovac m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV Bayern Munich. Trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 46 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i cho Robert Lewandowski. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern m\u00f9a sau b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p l\u1eddi m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o t\u1eeb Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 27 HLV Bayern gieo s\u1ea7u cho Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 27 HLV Bayern gieo s\u1ea7u cho Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-27-ngay-dau-nham-chuc-hlv-bayern-da-gieo-sau-cho-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kovac kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Lewy \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern m\u00f9a sau</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u00e2y! B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Daley Blind n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi MU.</strong> Ajax mu\u1ed1n mua Daley Blind t\u1eeb MU. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 8 \u0111\u1ebfn 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd De Telegraaf ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho, Pogba s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U. </strong>Nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Duncan Castles c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Sunday Times tin r\u1eb1ng Paul Pogba s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p gi\u1eefa ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Hazard t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Messi, Ronaldo. </strong>Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Eden Hazard t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Ronaldo hay Messi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Argentina x\u00e1ch vali v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard vs Panama\" title=\"Hazard vs Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/hazard-chelsea-phai-chi-dam-moi-giu-duoc-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hazard trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>PSG s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng si\u00eau th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. </strong>Sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Gianluigi Buffon \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Juventus sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3. \u0110\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 40 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 PSG sau khi \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Rashford: \"N\u1ebfu Anh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 11m t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m\". </strong>Marcus Rashford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 11m khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam mai (3/7), Tam s\u01b0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Colombia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HLV Mexico lo s\u1ee3 t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brazil.</strong> HLV Osorio hi\u1ec3u kh\u00e1 r\u00f5 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil. \u00d4ng t\u1eebng n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n \u1edf Sao Paulo tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean d\u1eabn d\u1eaft El Tri. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Mexico \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 Brazil \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3945","checkdouble":"190203"},{"date":"20:04 02/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Pogba s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/18/fred-se-giup-pogba-toa-sang-tai-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n binh Fred s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i M.U. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Gilberto Silva v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Fred gia nh\u1eadp M.U</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan United ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c cho ra m\u1eaft ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred t\u1eeb Shakhtar Donetsk (Ukraine) v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ee5c ng\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1eeb khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 k\u1ebft th\u00fac, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Diogo Dalot t\u1eeb Porto.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Fred \u0111ang tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Brazil. Fred gia nh\u1eadp Shakhtar n\u0103m 2013 t\u1eeb CLB qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Internacional. Trong 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, anh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Fred s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Fred s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Tan-binh-Fred-se-giup-Pogba-toa-sang-tai-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Fred gia nh\u1eadp M.U v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nFred l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng, anh c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i l\u00fac c\u00f2n tung ra nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat xa tr\u00e1i ph\u00e1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p gi\u00fap Pogba th\u0103ng hoa</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U t\u1eeb Juventus, hi\u1ebfm khi Paul Pogba c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Gilberto Silva \u2013 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u1eebng danh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Fred tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ph\u1ee5 t\u00e1 \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba chua chac kip binh phuc de ra san tran gap Sevilla.\" title=\"Paul Pogba ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Sevilla.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/18/fred-se-giup-pogba-toa-sang-tai-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Silva tin Fred s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cFred l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa s\u1ed1 6 v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 8\u201d, Silva n\u00f3i tr\u00ean trang web ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Manchester United. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf c\u1ea3 2 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u vai tr\u00f2 kh\u00e1c nhau trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 box-to-box v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. S\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Fred th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y Pogba. V\u1edbi Fred, Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i ti\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd th\u00edch. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mong ch\u1edd s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa Fred, Matic v\u00e0 Pogba c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch HLV Mourinho s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ecd.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-tang-boc-mbappe-len-may-sau-tran-dai-thang-argentina-469-190086.html\">Pogba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng Mbappe</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-phan-phao-truoc-nhung-chi-trich-cua-cdv-phap-469-189872.html\">Pogba ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ban-gai-pogba-theo-doi-nguoi-yeu-thi-dau-tu-khan-dai-421-189749.html\">B\u1ea1n g\u00e1i Pogba theo d\u00f5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-san-sang-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-psg-172-189590.html\">MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n v\u1edbi PSG</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-len-tieng-bao-ve-griezmann-469-189503.html\">Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Griezmann</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3944","checkdouble":"190206"},{"date":"20:23 02/07","title":"Darmian \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/darmian-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-roi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Darmian l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi M.U. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111ang m\u1edf ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft m\u00ecnh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Darmian kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua, Matteo Darmian ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 8 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho Man United t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 17 tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. M\u00f9a 2015/16, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV khi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Louis van Gaal mua v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Torino v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 12,7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, d\u1ea7n d\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Darmian b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. Sau khi HLV Jose Mourinho l\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 y\u1ebfu. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c M.U t\u1eadu v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Diogo Dalot t\u1eeb Porto, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Darmian tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ea5t m\u00f9 m\u1ecbt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Darmian l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Darmian l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/Hau-ve-Darmian-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-roi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Dalot t\u1edbi M.U khi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Darmian m\u1edd m\u1ecbt</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDarmian c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U song g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n. Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111a n\u0103ng 28 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111ang xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong kho\u1ea3ng 1 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Juventus nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n mua Darmian. V\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Torino cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc vi\u1ec7c h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Darmian cua MU\" title=\"Darmian cua MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/darmian-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-roi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Darmian l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMan United l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp c\u0169ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d, Darmian l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi M.U tr\u00ean La Gazzetta dello Sport. \u201cT\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n. Juventus, Inter Milan, Napoli hay m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u2013 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i do m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u n\u00f3i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra (r\u1eddi M.U), t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111ang m\u1edf ra.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDarmian c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do kh\u00f4ng ra \u0111i t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i: \u201cT\u00f4i d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd chia tay, nh\u01b0ng Man United kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. H\u1ecd n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng v\u1eabn xem t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng d\u00f9 t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 trong 1 n\u0103m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho\u201d, anh n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fred-se-giup-pogba-toa-sang-tai-mu-172-190206.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Pogba s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bat-chap-mau-thuan-voi-mourinho-pogba-se-o-lai-mu-172-190197.html\">B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho, Pogba s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-nha-xac-nhan-mu-chuan-bi-co-tan-binh-thu-3-172-190176.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/gareth-bale-duoc-khuyen-bo-real-ve-voi-mu-172-190161.html\">Ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i khuy\u00ean Gareth Bale b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-mu-troi-chan-thanh-cong-fellaini-172-189961.html\">N\u00d3NG: M.U 'tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n' th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Fellaini</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3943","checkdouble":"190208"},{"date":"20:27 02/07","title":"Sao PSG b\u00e1o tin vui cho MU v\u00e0 Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/8/sao-psg-bao-tin-vui-cho-mu-va-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Adrien Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris do lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Tuchel.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Adrien Rabiot mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi PSG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Adrien Rabiot l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a PSG. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra s\u00e2n 33 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Ligue 1 v\u00e0 8 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Champions League. N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn anh c\u00f3 47 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n Adrien Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n Adrien Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/8/sao-psg-bao-tin-vui-cho-mu-va-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rabiot c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nAdrien Rabiot l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a PSG d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Unai Emery. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hay ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t, m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua anh ghi 4 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Adrien Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris do lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Tuchel.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1eb1ng Marco Verratti s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a PSG m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Julian Draxler c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n thay v\u00ec ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay PSG. Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Tuchel, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd r\u1eddi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU v\u00e0 Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u1ecfi mua Rabiot</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a PSG. Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Adrien Rabiot, nh\u01b0ng Barca v\u00e0 M.U m\u1edbi l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t khao h\u01a1n c\u1ea3.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca vs PSG Suarez Rabiot\" title=\"Barca vs PSG Suarez Rabiot\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/3/9/huyen-thoai-xavi-tien-cu-sao-psg-cho-barcelona.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU v\u00e0 Barca quan t\u00e2m Rabiot</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM.U \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Barca c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Iniesta. C\u1ea3 M.U v\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o HLV Thomas Tuchel, n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng n\u00e0y s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu c\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, Rabiot s\u1ebd ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c r\u1eddi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3942","checkdouble":"190209"},{"date":"20:44 02/07","title":"Arsenal chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/arsenal-chi-27-trieu-bang-mua-sao-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Cristian Pavon, HLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal quan t\u00e2m Cristian Pavon</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch h\u1ecfi mua m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a n\u0103ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Cristian Pavon c\u1ee7a Boca Juniors. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Argentina t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Cristian Pavon v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Cristian Pavon v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/arsenal-chi-27-trieu-bang-mua-sao-argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Pavon</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u1ede H\u00e8 2018, Arsenal v\u1eabn quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u1ed1i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Cristian Pavon, HLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristian Pavon l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1nh, \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c trung phong c\u1eafm. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 6 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 11 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 Pavon, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Arsenal s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. HLV Emery \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Boca Juniors.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Arsenal c\u00f3 Pavon</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Pavon v\u1edbi Boca Juniors v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Argentina s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1edd AS c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Argentina \u0111\u00f2i 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Pavon th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPovon v\u1eeba c\u00f9ng Argentina tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sampaoli trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n. Argentina c\u1ee7a Pavon v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ec3 thua 3-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Stephan Lichtsteiner. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang nh\u1eafm trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis c\u1ee7a Dortmund v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Lucas Torreira \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3941","checkdouble":"190210"},{"date":"23:18 02/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/chinh-thuc-arsenal-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-thu-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal mua Sokratis th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Dortmund, trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. Trung v\u1ec7 30 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, sau th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Leno v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lichtsteiner\r\n</h2><h2>Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Sokratis</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng tin Arsenal quan t\u00e2m trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis c\u1ee7a Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 6, sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Arsenal mua Sokratis v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17,6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Arsenal mua Sokratis v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17,6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/chinh-thuc-arsenal-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-thu-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Sokratis</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal mua Sokratis th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Dortmund, trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. Trung v\u1ec7 30 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, sau th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Leno v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lichtsteiner.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sokratis s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Arsenal, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 17,6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. \u1ede s\u00e2n Emirates c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 s\u1ebd m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 5.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sokratis s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p th\u1ee9 2 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates, sau Konstantinos Mavropanos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Dortmund c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal trong n\u0103m 2018, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Pierre Emerick Aubameyang.</p>\r\n<h2>Sokratis l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sokratis n\u0103m nay 30 tu\u1ed5i, anh l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Dortmund trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013, ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 130 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Bundesliga v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, anh t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Werder Bremen, AC Milan, Genoa v\u00e0 AEK Athens. Sokratis \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 79 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T Hy L\u1ea1p.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Laurent Koscielny bu\u1ed9c HLV Unai Emery ph\u1ea3i mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7, v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Sokratis s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Mustafi l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Dortmund \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mang t\u00ean Lucas Torreira t\u1eeb Sampdoria.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3940","checkdouble":"190220"},{"date":"14:12 02/07","title":"Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018, sao Morocco g\u00e2y tai n\u1ea1n ch\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi?","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/tro-ve-tu-world-cup-2018-sao-morocco-gay-tai-nan-chet-nguoi.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"3939","checkdouble":"190164"},{"date":"14:15 02/07","title":"Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Maradona treo th\u01b0\u1edfng 8.000 b\u1ea3ng truy t\u00ecm k\u1ebb tung tin m\u00ecnh ch\u1ebft","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/vua-bong-da-maradona-treo-thuong-8000-bang-truy-tim-ke-tung-tin-minh-chet.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Diego Maradona v\u1eeba treo th\u01b0\u1edfng 8.000 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 truy t\u00ecm k\u1ebb tung tin \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ebft. Trong tr\u1eadn Argentina th\u1eafng Nigeria 2-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Maradona \u0111\u00e3 \u0103n m\u1eebng qu\u00e1 sung t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadp vi\u1ec7n v\u00ec ng\u1ea5t x\u1ec9u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi Maradona \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb, c\u01b0 d\u00e2n m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u00f4n xao b\u1edfi 2 \u0111o\u1ea1n ghi \u00e2m b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c C\u1eadu b\u00e9 v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 qua \u0111\u1eddi. \u0110o\u1ea1n ghi \u00e2m th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i 57 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9t qu\u1ef5 v\u00ec tim m\u1ea1ch. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110o\u1ea1n ghi \u00e2m th\u1ee9 2 xoay quanh vi\u1ec7c th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 c\u00e1i ch\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Maradona \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean th\u1ec3 thao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. Ch\u1ec9 trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn, hai \u0111o\u1ea1n ghi \u00e2m v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Maradona \u0111\u1ed9t ng\u1ed9t qua \u0111\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebb tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/maradona.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c c\u00e0ng di\u1ec5n ra theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i h\u01a1n khi ch\u1ecb g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Maradona \u0111\u00e3 \u0111au kh\u1ed5 t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c suy s\u1ee5p v\u00ec t\u01b0\u1edfng em trai ch\u1ebft th\u1eadt. &ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c, l\u00e0m sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tung tin qu\u00e1i \u00e1c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady&rdquo;. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3 Maradona b\u1ee9c x\u00fac n\u00f3i: &ldquo;T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft&rdquo;. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c C\u1eadu b\u00e9 v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n cho c\u00f4 b\u1ed3 Rocio Oliva c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea5n an m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n s\u1ed1ng ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ng\u1ecfm c\u1ee7 t\u1ecfi nh\u01b0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u00f2n theo lu\u1eadt s\u01b0 ri\u00eang Matias Morla c\u1ee7a Maradona, b\u1ea5t lu\u1eadn v\u00ec nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng phao tin k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 v\u00f4 nh\u00e2n t\u00ednh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00ean \u00e1n. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 danh t\u00ednh k\u1ebb tung tin \u0111\u1ed3n&rdquo;, Matias kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean t\u1edd nh\u1eadt b\u00e1o Clarin, &ldquo;Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi ki\u1ec7n h\u1eafn ta ra t\u00f2a v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi tung tin th\u1ea5t thi\u1ec7t, g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3938","checkdouble":"190165"},{"date":"15:45 02/07","title":"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</h2><h2>HLV HAGL ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a HAGL  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a HAGL  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec HAGL kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt 1/7, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n song ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n v\u00e0i sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 2, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng d\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \"B\u00e0n thua tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u1eafm. \u1ede hi\u1ec7p 1, hai \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 tho\u00e1t thua trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft n\u1eafng n\u00f3ng \u1edf Tam K\u1ef3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhanh ch\u00f3ng xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c trong hi\u1ec7p 2. Hai b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ec1u xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb hai bi\u00ean v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Th\u1eadt ti\u1ebfc khi HAGL ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u tung ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi 100% n\u1ed9i binh. Song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu l\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng HAGL n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \"Trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, BHL \u0111\u01b0a ra h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 n\u1ed9i binh. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u1ec1 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 3 tr\u00ean BXH. L\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 5 v\u1edbi 24 \u0111i\u1ec3m, k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 l\u00e0 Thanh H\u00f3a 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u1ea7n ch\u1eaft chiu h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-quang-nam-22-hagl-cu-dup-cua-van-toan-168-190109.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/van-toan-ghi-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-quang-nam-22-hagl-cu-dup-cua-van-toan-168-190109.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 HAGL: C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br />\r\nTi\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/quang-nam-vs-hagl-vleague-2018-372-190082.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/ket-qua-quang-nam-vs-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/quang-nam-vs-hagl-vleague-2018-372-190082.html\">Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 HAGL (KT): D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i Tam K\u1ef3</span><br />\r\nD\u00f9 c\u00f3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC, tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ebft th\u00fac 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c HAGL ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i chia \u0111i\u1ec3m 2-2 v\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dao-rimario-da-co-ben-do-moi-sau-khi-chia-tay-hagl-168-190063.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/tien-dao-rimario-da-co-ben-do-moi-sau-khi-chia-tay-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dao-rimario-da-co-ben-do-moi-sau-khi-chia-tay-hagl-168-190063.html\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi sau khi chia tay HAGL?</span><br />\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb CLB HAGL thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1i V-League. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3937","checkdouble":"190172"},{"date":"16:43 02/07","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 17 V-League: H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL chia \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/du-am-vong-17-vleague-ha-noi-tien-sat-ngoi-vuong-hagl-chia-diem-dang-tiec.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HAGL ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u1edf v\u00f2ng 17 V-League.</h2><h2>1. H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf khi ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tuy nhi\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng sau 17 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1edbm sau pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh Vinicius \u1edf ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 8 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng b\u1eb1ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng sau c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh L\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 31. 5 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 V\u0103n Ki\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 t\u1edbi h\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ngay t\u1ea1i C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u1edf ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 44 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp sau l\u00e0 Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a BVN \u0111\u1ebfn 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m, m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch qu\u00e1 an to\u00e0n cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 17 V-League H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL chia \u0111i\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 17 V-League H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL chia \u0111i\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/a00-8311-1530455756.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc 5 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. HAGL b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 17 V-League, CLB HAGL c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang gi\u1eef ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Qu\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Claudecir kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1 l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, khi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng, &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng v\u00e0i ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khi\u1ebfn HAGL \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi Tam K\u1ef3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f2a tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, CLB HAGL&nbsp;v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Qu\u1ea3ng Nam tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Pleiku \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 5 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi 24 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. SLNA l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 6<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 5 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, CLB SLNA kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ed1p 3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn sau v\u00f2ng 17 V-League, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00fang 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, SLNA ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n tr\u00ean BXH tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SLNA thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong th\u1eddi gian qua c\u0169ng nh\u1edd v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. Sau hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i L\u1ea1ch Tray b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 3-0&nbsp;\u1edf ph\u00fat 69 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c 3-2 trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i L\u1ea1ch Tray.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e0y, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hai Phong vs SLNA\" title=\"H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs SLNA\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/nhan-dinh-hai-phong-vs-slna-17h00-ngay-17-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>SLNA \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng t\u1ea1i L\u1ea1ch Tray</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. S\u00e0i G\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00eam c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u00edt sao 1-0 nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Thanh H\u00f3a L\u00ea Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 90 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean BXH m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00eam quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a CLB tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng an to\u00e0n. L\u00fac n\u00e0y S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 h\u01a1n TP.HCM 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf l\u1ea1i V-League m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2019.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/1/Highlight-Quang-Ninh-vs-Ha-Noi.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH sau vong 17 V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH sau v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/BXH-sau-vong-17-V-League-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH sau v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-quang-nam-22-hagl-cu-dup-cua-van-toan-168-190109.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/van-toan-ghi-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-quang-nam-22-hagl-cu-dup-cua-van-toan-168-190109.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 HAGL: C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\">HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-190140.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-190140.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 thua t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3936","checkdouble":"190182"},{"date":"16:39 02/07","title":"Salah k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Liverpool, t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/salah-chinh-thuc-ky-hop-dong-dai-han-voi-liverpool.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Salah \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2023.</h2><h2>Salah gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Liverpool, Real b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Salah \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool trao cho m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 5 n\u0103m sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSalah \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 44 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng sau khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Liverpool t\u1eeb Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36.9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n nh\u01b0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool, t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Salah gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool, t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/salah-chinh-thuc-ky-hop-dong-dai-han-voi-liverpool.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Salah gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/salah-vi-sao-toi-toa-sang-o-liverpool-172-176203.html\" target=\"_blank\">Salah ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eaft x\u00edch quan tr\u1ecdng</span> gi\u00fap Liverpool c\u1ea1nh tranh danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQuan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Salah kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Real s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Salah m\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Liverpool. </div>\r\n<h2>Klopp vui m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Salah</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau khi Salah \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Liverpool, HLV Klopp t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0nh cho Salah l\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u00f3 c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n hai \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o Liverpool v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Anfield v\u00e0 th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tham v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Mo Salah cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Liverpool v\u00e0 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00ec n\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, vi\u1ec7c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y cho th\u1ea5y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn r\u00f5 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Salah v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Salah kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1eadu \u1ea5y cao h\u01a1n l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111o\u1ea1t c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 do c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u1eb1m trong m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mo Salah ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ra sao. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-karius-172-190092.html\">Liverpool \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Karius</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-tro-lai-vu-fekir-quyet-canh-tranh-voi-mu-172-190075.html\">Liverpool tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1ee5 Fekir, quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3935","checkdouble":"190174"},{"date":"16:58 02/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/8/nguoi-nha-xac-nhan-mu-chuan-bi-co-tan-binh-thu-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia Craig Norwood, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tranh th\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 BL\u0110 Man United \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm ch\u1ed1t t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lee Grant \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 do, sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Stoke.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay 35 tu\u1ed5i, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh ra t\u1ea1i Anh n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 3 t\u1ea1i Old Trafford \u2013 sau David De Gea v\u00e0 Sergio Romero. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n cho r\u1eb1ng Grant s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf De Gea ra \u0111i c\u0169ng s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf, khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh T\u00e2y Ban Nha chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, M.U s\u1ebd g\u1eedi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Joel Pereira cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 21 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh mu\u1ed1n CLB cho m\u00ecnh \u0111i \u201cdu h\u1ecdc\u201d. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, M.U c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, n\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o g\u1eedi anh sang \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Nguoi-nha-xac-nhan-MU-chieu-mo-Lee-Grant-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia Craig Norwood, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a CLB \u2013 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh Lee Grant trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o m\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Norwood \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 t\u00e2n binh Fred v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot \u2013 ch\u1ec9 1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi CLB \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao 1m93 v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 35 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho Man United. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau, v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Romero \u0111\u1ebfn nay v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia-176-190157.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia-176-190157.html\">M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba Serbia</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Lazio.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu-172-190097.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu-172-190097.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Martial n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi MU?</span><br>\r\nBayern Munich mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Old Trafford nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool-172-190006.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool-172-190006.html\">MU mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span><br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t The Kop, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi \u0111\u1ee7 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3934","checkdouble":"190176"}]}